Qwen2.5-VL-3B / 7B — open-weight VLM; supports image and video/frame-sequence understanding.

MedGemma 1.5 4B — medical-oriented image-text VLM; useful for medical image interpretation, but not primarily a surgical video model.

LLaVA / LLaVA-Med — classic single-image VLM baselines for frame-level surgical description.

Video-LLaVA / LLaVA-NeXT-Interleave — LLaVA-style models with image + video / multi-frame support.

BLIP-2 / InstructBLIP — image captioning and VQA baselines; mainly for single-frame analysis.